25. A receiver comprising: 
at least two receive antennas 
a filter bank of linear filters having a first input coupled to an output of each receive antenna and a second input, said filter bank for equalizing signal vectors received over sub-channels of a multipath channel into signal vectors of a single channel; 
a channel estimator having an input coupled to an output of each receive antenna and an output coupled to the second input of the filter bank; 
a plurality of joint detectors in parallel with one another, each joint detector having an input coupled to an output of the filter bank and an output coupled to a decoder, each joint detector for detecting one of bits or symbols according to one spreading code; 
a chip-to-symbol down-converter, a de-scrambler, and a de-spreader, each disposed between the filter bank and the plurality of joint detectors.

